<p>

Gyve aims to link donors with people experiencing homelessness to help provide an overlooked and underfunded need, <b>transportation</b>. Lack of a metro card can be an insurmountable barrier to individuals looking to access food, health care and job programs. 
We work with case workers who present you, the donor, with their clients who need a MetroCard in order to access social services. You can donate a whole montly card or join our community of givers and contribute to part of a montly card. 
<a href="/signup">Click here to join</a>

<br><br><br>
Are you a case worker? Let us know who your clients are and where they're trying to go and our community will join forces and funds to provide them with a monthly MetroCard. 
